 al of Gender Thought and Expression&#160\;  Presentations addressing quee
 r worldbuilding\, attacks on higher education\, and more  "Destroy the Fa
 mily to Realize its Promise: Abolition as Care Communization\," a keynote
  presentation by critical utopianist scholar Sophie Lewis (https://colleg
 e.lclark.edu/departments/gender_studies/symposium/45th-annual-gender-stud
 ies-symposium/speakers/)  Times\, locations\, and additional details can 
 be found on the schedule (https://college.lclark.edu/departments/gender_s
 tudies/symposium/45th-annual-gender-studies-symposium/schedule/). Events 
 are free and open to the public.
