 nter for Animal Law Studies for this special event to kick off Animal Law
  Week. In 2024\, Lucy's Project convened a National Roundtable on Domesti
 c and Family Violence Perpetrated against People and Animals. This presen
 tation will share the Roundtable findings and recommendations for legisla
 tive\, policy and program reform to improve the safety and wellbeing of p
