 Spiritual Life and Chaplain to all<br />\n  <a href="mailto:hmhiman@lclar
 k.edu">hmhiman@lclark.edu<br />\n  <br />\n  503-768-7082</a>\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join the 2026 Spring Cohort of Awakened Awaren
 ess and get a <strong>$25 gift card</strong> to learn mindfulness and med
 itation! Participants engage in an 8 week evidence-based curriculum desig
 ned by neuroscientist Dr. Lisa Miller from Teachers College\, Columbia Un
 iversity. Engage in mindfulness techniques\, experience guided meditation
 s\, and discuss spiritual concepts. Learn tools and strategies to reduce 
 anxiety\, depression\, and post-traumatic stress and find ease and meanin
 g.<br />\n  <br />\n  Register <a href="https://forms.gle/G7UcVNKrjb3P3bG
 x5">here</a>!\n</p>
