SUMMARY:March Hand-Sewing Social with SCRAP PDX
DESCRIPTION:Join us to hand-sew decorative plush to welcome the new leaves with our friends from SCRAP PDX! Sew spring flowers\, birds\, raindrops\, and more. ✨ Bring a friend! Make a friend! Grab a beverage\, browse the books\, and gather round to sew some sweet spring things to celebrate the equinox. \nTraceable templates & embroidery stitch print-outs provided. Self-guided & beginner-friendly. A SCRAP educator will be ready to assist newer sewists with hand-sewing basics. \nThis is a ticketed event. Drop-ins welcome. Get tickets here.
