X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join the Center of Social Change in collaborat
 ion with an emerging local Portland nonprofit organization 'Common Lens'
  to learn about houselessness in our local community. We will be watching
  a short film on houselessness in Portland and it's overlap with substanc
 e abuse. Kelly Clendenon\, the director of the film and founder of Common
  Lens\, will be providing a Q &amp\; A session after the film. Snacks wil
 l be provided!<br />\n  <br />\n  <a class="btn-small-style-1" href="http
 s://www.givepulse.com/event/846018" target="_blank" rel="noopener">REGIST
 ER HERE!</a>\n</p>
