SUMMARY:Board Games @ Mox
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nCome learn new games and meet new people\, every Thursday evening.\n\nBoard games a plenty\, feel free to bring some -- usually a couple of us do\, and the Venue has a large library.\n\nWe play mostly lighter and middle weight games\, but sometimes heavier ones -- from Sushi Go to Dune Imperium. But I have seen everything from Mantis to Viticulture.\n\nPlease ask questions in the comments\, and let people know what board games you will bring and/or want to play.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pdxgames/events/313457140/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260221T024029Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T024029Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/f/5/5/600_519903925.jpeg
END:VEVENT
