SUMMARY:An easy 4–6 miles followed by $5 pints. 
DESCRIPTION:Portland Running Co. Weekly Group Runs\nYour host Brendan will lead you on an easy-ish run in the neighborhood or around the waterfront. After the run we return to the Run Pub for libations and yakkety-yak. You'll come back.\n\nNo sign up necessary\, but if you haven't joined a PRC run before\, the host will have you sign an e-waiver beforehand. Ages 21 and over for this run\, please. Also\, no dogs. (Sorry\, we love 'em\, but there have been incidents....)\n\nMore: https://portlandrunning.com/pages/weekly-group-runs
