 rical artifacts\, and community\, we'll explore how open rescue challenge
 s industrial animal agriculture and advances justice for animals. Refresh
 ments provided by Vtopian Artisan Cheeses. There will also be a silent Au
 ction benefiting Lighthouse Farm Sanctuary. RSVP <a href="https://engage.
 lclark.edu/register/AnimalLawWeekReception2026">here.</a>&#160\;\n</p>
