SUMMARY:Relax and Recharge Movie Fridays at the SE VRC
DESCRIPTION:From noon to 4 pm every Friday of winter term\, come watch a 
 movie or two\, eat popcorn\, drink soda\, and enjoy other snacks. It is a
  time set aside to unwind from our hectic weeks\, not focusing on anythin
 g but being entertained. Movies are typically selected day of the event\,
  so come in a little early with a suggestion.Find the Veterans Resource C
 enter at the Southeast Campus Mount Tabor Hall Room 120.—Event Details:
  https://hub.pcc.edu/rsvp?id=382151 (https://hub.pcc.edu/rsvp?id=382151)
