X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  <span data-sheets-root="1">If you plan to take
  the MPRE in March\, here's an opportunity for you to take a simulated ex
 am. Helix Bar Review will provide the exams and create a testing environm
 ent for you right on campus. To participate\, in addition to registering 
 on this page\, you will need to do the following:</span>\n</p>\n<ol>\n  <
 li>Register <a href="https://go.helixbarreview.org/l/992142/2026-02-17/23
 763y">HERE</a> by Wednesday\, March 11.\n  </li>\n  <li>Enroll in <a href
 ="https://enroll.helixbarreview.org/helix-mpre/">Helix MPRE 2025/2026</a>
  (for free) no later than Thursday\, March 12.\n  </li>\n  <li>Show up on
  Friday\, March 13 @ 1:00PM in McCarty Classroom 4 with your laptop and c
 harging cord to complete the Simulated exam within Helix MPRE. It will be
  2 hours well spent!\n  </li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  If you have any questions\, 
 or need assistance enrolling in the Helix MPRE course\, please do not hes
 itate to contact Kristine Browne (<a href="mailto:kbrowne@helixbarreview.
 org">kbrowne@helixbarreview.org</a>).\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span data-sheets-roo
 t="1">&#160\;</span>\n</p>
