SUMMARY:Maple-Wildwood Loop + Coffee! 🍀
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\nJoin us for a scenic loop from the **LOWER Saltzman Trailhead**! We’ll climb **Saltzman**\, take a right on **Maple**\, then right on **Leif**. From there\, it’s a left on **FL5** to **Wildwood**\, cruising until we drop down **Koenig**. We’ll finish with a left on **Leif**\, right on **FL4**\, and a final left on **Maple** back to the trailhead — about **6.3 miles** total.\n\n**The route**\nView the route on [AllTrails](https://www.alltrails.com/explore/map/maple-ww-no-bridge-f0b1d58?u=i&sh=bjqei2).\n\n*Want a shorter option?* Try the Maple-Leif-Saltzman loop at **3.16 miles** ([route here](https://www.alltrails.com/explore/map/map-august-17-2025-88f0bf2?u=i&sh=bjqei2)).\n\n**Where to meet**\nMeet at the LOWER Saltzman Trailhead. As with any trailhead\, practice good car hygiene and mind your valuables.\n\nWe start running at 8:35\, so please plan accordingly!\n\n**What to bring**\n\n* Grippy trail running shoes\n* Coffee cup/travel mug\n\n**Afterwards**\nWe will have post-run coffee and some St. Patty’s day goodies 🌈🍀\n\nIf you’d like\, bring a snack to share or chip in a couple bucks to the coffee fund (Venmo: @JeffMonaghanPDX). No pressure — just come enjoy the run and community.\n\nSee you there!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-trail-runners-group/events/313591914/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260301T205747Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T205747Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/2/0/f/0/600_532988432.jpeg
END:VEVENT
