SUMMARY:Coffee and sketch at Coffeehouse Five 
DESCRIPTION:Portland Coffee & Sketch Club\nAll skill levels are welcome! If you're working on a technique and need some help\, other members are always helpful and encouraging.\n\nDon't let lack of supplies stop you! I bring some extra supplies just in case. Guests are welcome! Drop in welcome! Don't worry about running late. We're usually at the coffee shop for a couple extra hours.\n\nThis café has been very welcoming of our group\, they have a comfortable interior\, a full coffee-bar\, and a small selection of food-items (muffins\, cookies\, and sandwiches)\, and they do have wi-fi. Bring your art-supplies and whatever you'd like to work on\, or sketch your surroundings! As always\, they serve food here so let's refrain from bringing anything that is really messy or toxic.\n\nOur club is a safe-space. We Welcome ALL Skill-Levels\, ALL Races and Ethnicities\, ALL Religions\, ALL Countries of Origin\, ALL Gender Identities\, ALL Sexual Orientations\, ALL Abilities & Disabilities\, ALL Spoken Languages\, ALL Ages\,.. Everyone!\n\nI look forward to drawing with you!
