SUMMARY:Family Hike: Explore Mt. Tabor with Portland Active Dads!
DESCRIPTION:Portland Active Dads\nCalling all Portland Active Dads for a fun-filled family adventure at Mt. Tabor! Join us for a memorable day of hiking through scenic landscapes\, bonding with your kids\, and enjoying the great outdoors. This event is perfect for both single dads and those with families looking to connect with like-minded individuals who value outdoor activities. Whether you're a seasoned hiker or new to the trails\, this is a relaxed and inclusive event suitable for all experience levels. Don't miss out on this opportunity to enjoy quality time with your kids while exploring the beauty of nature!
