 rrega\, and works by Astor Piazzolla. Also featured is a piece written by
  Michael Stirling\, rooted in Indian classical music traditions. The prog
 ram highlights the development from Romantic traditions to the rhythmic a
 nd stylistic innovations of Nuevo Tango\, showcasing a wide range of expr
 essive possibilities within the instrument's repertoire.</p><p>  This per
 formance will be <a href="https://vimeo.com/event/4079258" target="_blank
 " rel="noopener">live streamed here.</a></p><p>  &#160\;</p><p><strong>Pa
