 Spiritual Life and Chaplain<br />\n  hmhiman@lclark.edu\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  <strong>Is living in this time A LOT? Let's se
 t aside our saturated thinking brains for 90 minutes and move into our bo
 dy's wisdom.</strong>\n</p>
