SUMMARY: Shamrock Special Steam Train Ride
DESCRIPTION:All aboard for St. Paddy’s fun! Don’t miss your chance to cel
 ebrate St. Patrick’s Day in unforgettable style at the Oregon Rail Herita
 ge Center!\n\nClimb aboard for a 45-minute festive steam train adventure 
 along the Willamette River—complete with St. Patrick’s Day décor and fun 
 kids’ activities.\n\nFeel the thrill as the legendary Polson No. 2 roars 
 to life in steam! Take in sweeping riverside views from our open-air car\
 , or stay warm and cozy in our enclosed\, heated coaches. Wear your green
  and bring your Irish spirit—this ride is only here once a year!\n\nWhen:
  Saturday\, March 14 & Sunday\, March 15\n\nDeparture Times: 12:00pm | 1:
 30pm | 3:00pm | 4:30pm\n\nTickets: Adults $24 | Seniors & Military $21.50
  | Children $17 | Infants (under 3) FREE | Family Pass $74 (2 Adults & 2 
 Children)\n\nSeats are limited! Secure your spot now and make this St. Pa
 ddy’s weekend one to remember.
CATEGORIES:Train-Ride,Kid-Friendly,Family-Fun,St.-Patrick's-Day
