URL:https://tockify.com/kptv.calendar/detail/2000/1773612000000
SUMMARY: Northwest Vocal Arts Presents the Music of Brazil in a Community
  Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Cordilheira: Range of the Americas-the Music of Brazil\n\nNWV
 A's March concert will be our annual performance of music from the Southe
 rn Hemisphere. Titled Cordilheira: Range of the Americas\, this concert w
 ill make your spirit soar as we journey through the sounds\, rhythms\, an
 d soul of Brazil.\n\nMore than a concert\, Cordilheira is a cultural cele
 bration blending choral music\, Brazilian percussion\, and heartfelt comm
 unity connection.\n\nThe concert will feature the NWVA professional Olymp
 ia Chamber Choir and the NWVA Evergreen Youth Choir performing stunning c
 horal works including Bendita Sabedoria by Brazil's greatest composer\, H
 eitor Villa-Lobos\, and two works by Carlos Alberto Pinto Fonseca\, Muie 
 Rendera\, a setting of two of the most popular folk tunes from Northeast 
 Brazil with percussion accompaniment and based on the Brazilian rhythm ba
 ião and Jubiabá\, an evocation of a candomblé ceremony.\n\nPre- and post-
  concert celebrations include DJ Ju Borba https://www.instagram.com/_borb
 a/?hl=en setting the tone with a Brazilian soundtrack\, followed by a joy
 ful Brazilian reception\, with Santa Terra Bakery https://santaterrabaker
 y.com/ serving authentic Brazilian sweets and savory bites\, Nossa Famíli
 a Coffee https://www.nossacoffee.com/?srsltid=AfmBOorsNyJdU9Hf8gkvov3OTcf
 s4AEKIWOQv57mMKQ1lm93QyxssXIz providing freshly brewed Brazilian coffee\,
  and the BrazilTones https://new.express.adobe.com/webpage/Ny4ZbDGU5M7ur 
 performing bossa nova and MPB favorites. The reception is produced by GIN
 GA Events https://www.comginga.com/ .\n\nJoin us for an afternoon of harm
 ony\, rhythm\, and flavor - an invitation to experience the beauty and wa
 rmth of Brazil through music\, food and celebration.\n\nGeneral admission
  is $35 ($15 for students). Tickets may be purchased here https://www.eve
 ntbrite.com/e/1612889268219?aff=oddtdtcreator .
CATEGORIES:Brazilian-music,Choral-music
X-TKF-FEATURED-IMAGE:https://d3flpus5evl89n.cloudfront.net/62191926b9407b
 526addc41f/69669ae35f079359c6c8e9d9/scaled_1024.jpg
X-TKF-CUSTOM-PREVIEW:Cordilheira: Range of the Americas-the Music of Braz
