SUMMARY:Play without Borders - games from around the world
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Veterans Resource Center for a new event calle
 d "Play Without Borders"\, every Tuesday at noon. Veterans come from dive
 rse backgrounds\, cultures\, and experiences. This is a multicultural gam
 e day designed to bring students together through fun\, friendly competit
 ion and shared experience. This event celebrates the diverse cultures wit
 hin our campus and community by featuring games from around the world!Tue
 sday Feb 3rd Play Mexican Bingo!Let's create a safe space for students an
 d veterans alike to come together\, share our experiences\, and learn gam
 es from different countries in order to become more intertwined within ou
 r communities.Play\, learn\, and connect while enjoying good company and 
 community spirit!—Event Details: https://hub.pcc.edu/rsvp?id=382171 (ht
 tps://hub.pcc.edu/rsvp?id=382171)
