CATEGORIES:Lecture,Performing Arts,Community
DESCRIPTION:Brain Awareness Week: Neural HarmonyJoin the Psychology and Mus
 ic Departments on Tuesday\, March 17 at 6:00PM in PAB 320 for this Brain Aw
 areness Week event exploring how music and neuroscience work together. The 
 evening will feature a short performance by Reed's Collegium Musicum follow
 ed by a conversation examining how the brain perceives\, processes\, and is
  transformed by music.  Made possible by neuroscientists Angelica Nicolacou
 dis ('25) and Assistant Professor of Psychology Valeria González\, Reed Col
 lege neuroscience Maya Franzen ('28) and Isara Moriya ('28)\, students of C
 ollegium Musicum\, and Assistant Professor of Music Shohei Kobayashi.
