X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join us for "Housing &amp\; Food Insecurity mi
 xer" where Lewis &amp\; Clark students can meet and connect with the UB s
 tudents participating in an immersion trip to Portland focused on housing
  and food insecurity. Come chat\, mingle\, and swap perspectives on how t
 hese issues show up in different communities\, including comparisons betw
 een Buffalo\, NY and Portland\, as well as experiences within the LC comm
 unity. We'll also talk about challenges\, local solutions\, and what supp
 ort can look like on and off campus.\n</p>
