SUMMARY:Leif-Alder-Aspen (or Wild Cherry) Loop - Eve Run ed.
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\n**Wed Eve Run in Forest Park!**\n\n**Start on** **Leif Erickson** **with a steady climb to** **Alder****\, then turn right for another climb up to** **Wildwood****. Turning left\, follow Wildwood as it winds along\, then turn left down** **Aspen** **back to** **Leif****. From there\, return to the start at the** **Thurman Gate** **for a total of** **6 miles****.**\n\n**The Route** **(Segment 1):** [AllTrails](https://www.alltrails.com/explore/custom-routes/leif-alder-aspen-or-wildcherry-loop-69853b6)\n***Want a shorter option?*** **Check out Segment 2 -- Continue up** **Keil** **Trail from Wildwood/Alder\, connecting to** **Wild Cherry** **and take Wild Cherry all the way down to** **Leif** **\\- back to start\\. Total just shy of** **4 miles**\n\n**Meetup:** **Let's meet at the Thurman gate\, and we'll head out from there on Leif. Practice good car hygiene and mind your valuables! We will start running at 6:37pm PST.**\n\n**Bring:**\n\n* **Grippy trail running shoes**\n* **Headlamp - just in case**\n\n**After:** **Group kudos and home**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-trail-runners-group/events/313682975/
