X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Please join us on <strong data-index-in-node="
 18" data-path-to-node="5">Thursday\, March 19th\, at 10:00 AM</strong> as
  we gather at the <strong>Alumni Gatehouse Patio</strong> to dedicate a m
 emorial bench in honor of Oliver Milavetz.\n</p>\n<p data-path-to-node="6
 ">\n  While Oliver's birthday is March 20th\, we have chosen to gather on
  the 19th to better allow for his friends\, classmates\, and the L&amp\;C
  community to attend and reflect together. Our hope is to establish this 
 as a lasting space for connection and "Oliverness" on our campus.\n</p>\n
 <p data-path-to-node="15">\n  This will be a casual\, open space to refle
 ct and connect. We'll be honoring Oliver's birthday with <strong data-ind
 ex-in-node="99" data-path-to-node="15">cupcakes and wishes</strong>\, alo
 ngside a <strong data-index-in-node="132" data-path-to-node="15">river ro
 ck painting activity</strong>. Paint a stone to leave at the bench as a l
 asting tribute\, or take one home with you.\n</p>\n<p data-path-to-node="
 16">\n  If you cannot make it at 10:00 AM\, we encourage you to visit the
  bench at the Alumni Gatehouse Patio at any time during the day to share 
 a quiet moment or leave a memory.<br />\n  <br />\n  <strong data-index-i
 n-node="0" data-path-to-node="8">RSVP:</strong> To help us ensure we have
  enough supplies and refreshments for everyone\, please let us know if yo
 u plan to attend:<br />\n  <a title="https://engage.lclark.edu/register/?
 id=fc19af12-c9ee-4b59-b0f9-65d2f5f7e3e8" href="https://engage.lclark.edu/
 register/?id=fc19af12-c9ee-4b59-b0f9-65d2f5f7e3e8" target="_blank" rel="n
 oopener">RSVP via this link</a><br />\n  <br />\n  Sincerely\,<br />\n  A
 lumni and Parent Engagement Office Team\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-TAGS:alumni|In-person Event
END:VEVENT
