SUMMARY:Trail Running Film Fest 2026!
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\nJoin us at **The Mountain Shop** on **Thursday\, March 19th from 6:30-8:30pm** for the ***Trail Running Film Festival*** Portland stop! The TRFF is a collaborative festival that focuses on an equitable future where everyone is celebrated on trails and within our broader trail running culture.\n\nThis will be a selection of films from multiple filmmakers\, who all celebrate running as a universal practice to explore our collective and individual potential to pursue our wildest dreams.\n\n**Buy your Tickets here!** https://www.eventbrite.com/e/mountain-shop-presents-the-trail-running-film-festival-tickets-1983922266906?aff=oddtdtcreator\n\n**New Store Location:**\n**Mountain Shop**\n**1205 NE 33rd Ave.**\n**Portland\, OR 97232**
