DESCRIPTION:Hey Seniors! Grab a slice of pizza and get advice on all things
  thesis at Slice & Advice. Staff from the Library\, Computer User Services\
 , Instructional Technology\, Visual Resource Center\, Printing Services\, a
 nd the Registrar will be on hand to answer questions about your thesis proc
 ess. Drop by and get advice on research\, the thesis template\, formatting\
 , citation management\, using images & copyright\, submitting & printing yo
 ur thesis\, and any other questions you may have.\n\n \n\nCan't make it? Se
 nd your questions to Ask A Librarian at library@reed.edu
