SUMMARY:SBC Portland x Bold Coffee & Books
DESCRIPTION:Silent Book Club Portland\n📚✨ Silent Book Club Portland – March Meetup! ✨📚\n\nOur next Silent Book Club Portland gathering is happening next weekend!\n\nAs always\, the format is simple:\n✨ Bring any book you’d like\n✨ Read silently for about an hour\n✨ Stay after to chat\, share recommendations\, or simply enjoy the cozy reading vibe\n\nSince International Women’s Day just passed (March 8th)\, let’s celebrate by bringing a book written by a woman if you can (‼️🥺)\, whether it’s a favorite author\, a new discovery\, or someone whose work you’ve been meaning to read. 💜\n\n🗓 Date: March 22nd\n⏰ Time: 2 pm\n📍 Location: Bold Coffee & Books\, 1755 SW Jefferson St\, Portland\, OR 97205\n\nBring a friend\, bring a book\, and let’s spend a cozy Sunday afternoon reading together. 📖✨ As always\, please remember to support our host by grabbing a drink or snack while you’re there! ☕️🥐 Can’t wait to see you all soon!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/silent-book-club-portland/events/313752057/
