SUMMARY:Monday Night Easy Run in Beaverton
DESCRIPTION:Portland Running Co. Weekly Group Runs\nJessa and Kristin are your leaders for Beaverton's easygoing Monday-night run/walk. All paces and abilities welcome. Weather-permitting\, we'll use the Fanno Creek Trail\, but alternative neighborhood routes are the norm during winter and into spring.\n\nDistances vary\, but usually 3–5 miles. Lights and reflective clothing are recommended. No charge for this run\, like all PRC group runs: https://portlandrunning.com/pages/weekly-group-runs.\n\nAll are welcome\, but no dogs please.
