CREATED:20260210T195911Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260210T195911Z
UID:20950-1774353600-1774357200@www.thesquarepdx.org
SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Cosacchi at Less and More Coffee
DESCRIPTION:Cosacchi will be performing at Less and More Coffee on Downtown’s transit mall! \nCosacchi is an Indie Rock band from Portland\, OR. It was created by singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist Conor Adams in 2020. Their sound is heavily influenced by American Folk-Rock and Jazz music. Adam’s distinctive voice is a soothing element of the music\, together with the harmonies provided by vocalist Alena Bagoly they create a unique blend that comforts the listener. Songs range from laid-back talksing songwriting\, to high energy/guitar driven anthems. With Cosacchi\, there is truly a sound for every occasion. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-cosacchi-at-less-and-more-coffee/
LOCATION:Less & More Coffee\, 1003 SW 5th Ave\, Portland\, OR\, 97204\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/08-Cosacchi-Photo-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
