SUMMARY:Weekly Member Hour
DESCRIPTION:Members and their guests are invited to enjoy an exclusive hour in the garden in the early morning glow. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWednesdays\, 9:00–10:00 AM (Starting December 1\, 2025) \n\n\n\nThis exclusive hour allows members to take a quiet morning stroll through the garden as the city begins its day \n\n\n\nMembers are encouraged to bring guests in accordance with their membership level. This is a wonderful opportunity to introduce friends and family to Lan Su\, sharing the peaceful ambiance of the garden during these exclusive hours. \n\n\n\n\nExplore Membership
