SUMMARY:Inheritance of Orquidea Divina and discussion 
DESCRIPTION:It's more than just reading books\nLocation : TBD NW\, NE\, SE downtown Portland.\n\n_The Inheritance or Orquidea Divina_ by Zoraida Cordova\n\nDescription:\nThe Montoyas are used to a life without explanations. They know better than to ask why the pantry never seems to run low or empty\, or why their matriarch won’t ever leave their home in Four Rivers—even for graduations\, weddings\, or baptisms. But when Orquídea Divina invites them to her funeral and to collect their inheritance\, they hope to learn the secrets that she has held onto so tightly their whole lives. Instead\, Orquídea is transformed\, leaving them with more questions than answers.\n\nSeven years later\, her gifts have manifested in different ways for Marimar\, Rey\, and Tatinelly’s daughter\, Rhiannon\, granting them unexpected blessings. But soon\, a hidden figure begins to tear through their family tree\, picking them off one by one as it seeks to destroy Orquídea’s line. Determined to save what’s left of their family and uncover the truth behind their inheritance\, the four descendants travel to Ecuador—to the place where Orquídea buried her secrets and broken promises and never looked back.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/itsmorethanjustreadingbooks/events/312921267/
