CREATED:20260116T233604Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T233604Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/4/3/1/600_532281553.jpeg
END:VEVENT
