SUMMARY:Scrap to Sparkle: Reimagined Glass Shards
DESCRIPTION:Portland Arts and Craft Meetup Group\nYour weekly creative workout starts here! Let's turn scraps into fused glass brilliance every Tuesday. Plates\, bowls\, jewelry\, sun catchers\, wall hangings and more! Your imagination is the limit here at Village Glass Studio. Learn a new skill every week and make Tuesdays your creative recharge.\n\nInterested in working on a larger masterpiece over a period of sessions? Ask about VGS's studio membership cards for kiln space and storage.\n\nWeekly sessions are $35 per person or 3 sessions for $85.\nIf possible\, please Venmo ahead of the event: @villageglassstudio\n\nWe so look forward to having you.
