DESCRIPTION:One lazy zinester's favorite way to bind! Let's make drum leaf-
 bound zines!\n\nDrum leaf binding is an adhesive-only method for binding pa
 ges together that lies flat\, lets you avoid dealing with rearranging sprea
 ds for printing\, and is just a really fun way to bind. It's great for bind
 ing things like photographs or art into a cute and chunky book.\n\nThis Ree
 d Zine Fest workshop is led by Sarah Joy Calpo and is being held in PAB 104
  (Performing Arts Building\, Room 104).
