SUMMARY:⏰Library Equipment DUE Monday\, Mar 23\, 2026! 📥 (COPY)
DESCRIPTION:⏰Library Equipment DUE Monday\, Mar 23\, 2026! &#128229\;Pa
 nthers\, this is a kind reminder that Equipment items borrowed from PCC L
 ibrary must be returned by the First Day of the Break of each term.&#1283
 12\;This term\, the due date is Monday\, Mar 23\, 2026.&#128313\;Equipmen
 t must be brought back to the same campus they were borrowed from and han
 ded to library staff directly.&#128313\;Larger equipment such as Laptops\
