SUMMARY:Whimsical Wilderness: Creating Ethereal Animal Portraits
DESCRIPTION:Portland Art Guild\n**PLEASE NOTE: Official signup is through our website:** [Portland Art Guild](https://portlandartguild.org/product/whimsical-wilderness-creating-ethereal-animal-portraits-march-23rd-30th-10am-2pm/)\n\n2-session series: $45 for PAG Members and $90/nonmembers.\nSessions from 10:00am to 2:00pm on March 23rd and 30th\, 2026\n\n**Step into a realm where nature meets the subconscious.** This class invites you to move beyond realism and explore the dreamlike intersection of wildlife and dreamy\, expressive landscapes. We will focus on capturing the “spirit” of an animal rather than just its anatomy. I will guide you through the techniques needed to place majestic creatures within soft\, glowing environments that feel like a memory or a myth.\n\nFind your supply list [here](https://portlandartguild.org/product/whimsical-wilderness-creating-ethereal-animal-portraits-march-23rd-30th-10am-2pm/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-fine-arts-guild/events/313379022/
