SUMMARY: One-Night-Only: An Evening with Chef Amanda Freitag at The Ritz-
 Carlton\, Portland
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an extraordinary culinary evening at Bellpine on 
 April 2nd.\n\nWe are honored to welcome nationally renowned chef Amanda F
 reitag\, who will collaborate with our Chef de Cuisine Jocelyn Chacón to 
 present a one‐of‐a‐kind gastronomic experience. The evening begins with a
  cocktail reception\, featuring canapés and a welcoming beverage. Guests 
 will then enjoy a five‐course tasting menu inspired by the vibrant bounty
  of spring in the Pacific Northwest\, and each course will be thoughtfull
 y paired with exclusive wine selections to enhance the dining experience.
  This intimate experience will take place in our private dining room over
 looking the Portland skyline\, offering a stunning backdrop for an unforg
 ettable evening.\n\nThis is a limited‐seating event. Reservations can be 
 made through OpenTable.\n\nWe are happy to accommodate dietary restrictio
 ns with 48 hours’ notice.
