SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – The BrazilTones at Less and More Coffee
DESCRIPTION:The BrazilTones will be performing at Less and More Coffee on Downtown’s transit mall! \nThe BrazilTones are Deborah Bayardino on vocals\, Ronnie Robins on guitar and vocals and Brian L. Davis on percussion. They embrace the beauty\, poetic lyrics and rhythmic wonder of Bossa Nova\, Samba and MPB (Música Popular Brasileira). They also perform original songs composed by Robins. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-the-braziltones-at-less-and-more-coffee/
