  0143" data-max-w="600" data-max-h="450" loading="lazy" data-optimized="t
 rue"/>\n</picture><em>Kim will also share a glimpse of his upcoming guide
 d trip to Ireland in September 2026\, where he'll lead travelers to Dubli
