BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"University Of Portland": "https://up.enterprise.localist.com/event/60th-annual-up-jazz-festival"}
X-SOURCE-ID:university_of_portland
X-SOURCE:University Of Portland
CATEGORIES:Performance,Social Gathering / Reception
DESCRIPTION:The University of Portland Jazz Festival showcases outstanding 
 student musicians\, guest artists\, and clinicians from around the country\
 , all contributing to a vibrant celebration of jazz performance and educati
 on on our campus. Since its inception\, the UP Jazz Festival has become a p
 remier student jazz event in the Pacific Northwest. We support a mission of
  excellent teaching and individual attention in an environment that fosters
  development of the whole person\, and our goal is to ensure that every par
 ticipant leaves the festival inspired\, with a greater appreciation for the
  art of jazz.\n\nThe UP Jazz Festival features a one-day\, non-competitive\
 , educational format for high school and middle school bands\, with "Outsta
 nding Soloist" awards given to students from each visiting band. We present
  the feature performance with our guest artist and the UP Jazz Ensemble\, a
 s well as our guest artist's master class\, during the day\, in order to en
 sure availability for visiting student groups who cannot attend an evening 
 concert.\n\nThe 2026 Jazz Festival will feature performances by student ens
 embles\, a clinic for each participating student group\, a master class wit
 h this year’s guest artist\, trumpeter Victor Garcia\, a concert featuring 
 the UP Jazz Ensemble with Mr. Garcia\, and an evening jam session with UP f
 aculty and students. \n\nSchedules will be updated here\, and we look forwa
 rd to seeing you on The Bluff!
DTSTAMP:20260312T160902Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260408
GEO:45.575097;-122.728206
LOCATION:Chiles Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:60th Annual UP Jazz Festival
