 oblpct/Pages/CCCE.aspx">Click here for more information</a></p><hr /><h2>
 <strong>Details &amp\; Registration</strong></h2><p style="line-height: 1
 .5\;"><strong>Date and Time:</strong> Wednesday\, April 8\, 2026\, 12-3 p
 .m. PST\, Online</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Presenter:</str
 ong>&#160\;Regina Wei\, LMFT</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Cos
 t and Credits:</strong> $79\, includes 3 CEUs. GSEC Alumni and Adjuncts s
 ave 20%. $40 student rate.</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;">  No-cost reg
 istrations available for GSEC Faculty\, Staff\, and Clinical Mental Healt
 h Supervisors. Email <a href="mailto:cce@lclark.edu">cce@lclark.edu</a> t
 o register.</p><p><a class="btn-small-style-1" href="https://lclark.tfafo
 rms.net/wf1W4MQ?epid=a1aUY0000022GCP" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Regi
 ster Online</a></p><div id="lw_widget_30f0017c" class="lw_widget lw_widge
 t_type_blurbs lw_widget_blurbs lw_widget_id_7119 lw_widget_accessibility_
 statement lw_widget_pagination"><ul class="lw_widget_results lw_widget_re
 sults_blurbs"><li class="lw_item_1"><div class="lw_blurbs_body"><p class=
 "p1" style="font-size: 15px\; line-height: 1.5\;"><em><strong>Accessibili
