DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Knot Binary: A Trans and Nonbinary Craft Circle and 
 Mutual Aid Outreach!! This is a weekly drop-in group for students on Thursd
 ays from 4:30PM-6:00PM to develop community and have space for processing\,
  all while making cute crafts! This semester Knot Binary will be doing mutu
 al aid outreach for LGBTQ+ houseless community members and will be working 
 together to create hats\, gloves and scarves. This group is hosted by HCC t
 herapists: Skylar Willson-Ko\, LMFT and Sarah Fleischauer\, LPC. Beverages 
 and snacks will be provided as well as patterns\, yarn\, crochet hooks and 
 knitting needles! You are also welcome to bring your own crafts! The first 
 group to be hosted will be on January 29th\, 2026 (see posting for location
  details). Please email Skylar Willson-Ko with any questions at willsonkos@
 reed.edu.
DTEND:20260410T010000Z
