SUMMARY:Best of 90s & 2000s Dance Flashback -14th Anniversary Bash!
DESCRIPTION:To celebrate 14 years of Dance Flashback parties in the Crystal Ballroom building… we are throwing an anniversary “Best Of 90s and 2000s Bash!” A whole night full of nothing but bangers and crowd favorites! Wear your favorite 90s outfits\, 2000s gear\, glow in the dark accessories or just put on your best dance shoes and help us celebrate 14 years!  \nAnd this year we are adding a second floor of dancing! Our 2010s Night will be live all night long in Lola’s Room on the second floor. Both floors included with the Anniversary ticket.
