SUMMARY:The BIGGEST Clothing Swap in the Northwest
DESCRIPTION:The BIGGEST Clothing Swap in the Northwest!!! \nTwo full floors of swapping fun! \nBallroom on the 3rd Floor: The main swap area with tons of clothing sorted into non-binary categories as well as a plethora of shoes and accessories! Plus a bar! \nLola’s Room on the 2nd Floor: Plus-size swap with more shoes and accessories! \nA small entrance fee and a bag of clothes gets you a WHOLE NEW WARDROBE! You can bring more than one bag if you want! Don’t have a bag of clothes to share? No problem\, you can buy an empty bag for $5. \nPLEASE READ THE RULES VERY CAREFULLYCLOTHES MUST BE: \n\nCleanWearable\nNo holes\nNo odors\nNo underwear\, socks/ hosiery\, or bras (new items still in original packaging are okay)\nNo children’s apparel (sorry!)\n\nAnd\, Clothing Swap soundtrack provided by DJ Gregarious!!! \nInvite ALL your friends! The more that attend\, the more awesome clothes to choose from!!! \nThis is an all ages event\, but we recommend leaving small children at home.
URL:https://www.crystalballroompdx.com/events/275512-the-biggest-clothing-swap-in-the-northwest/
CATEGORIES:April
