 eedies. Participants will receive a nature-themed gift at the first session
 .\n\nWe will meet at GCC-A and then transition outdoors. \n\nA pre-screenin
 g phone appointment is required for participation in this group. To schedul
 e\, email facilitators Jenni Leatham\, LPC at jleatham@reed.edu or Miriam S
 aucedo\, LPC at msaucedo@reed.edu\, send a secure message via the portal\, 
 or call the HCC front desk at 503-777-7281.
