 n your expertise and how you can assist others.&#13\;\nAre you job hunti
 ng or hiring? Let us know!&#13\;\nCommunity events you wanna plug. If no
 ne\, that's cool too.&#13\;\n12:30 AM - Wrapping Up: You can stay longer
