 97103029?pwd=kCGXBO72hfCQjIoWk4vNQlEXgPj7St.1</a><br />The Student Basic 
 Needs Center invites you to join the Resilience &amp\; Resource Collectiv
 e\, a student-led group focused on housing\, finances\, and mental health
 . Listening counts. No shame. No fixing. Just collective wisdom and pract
 ical resources.<br />Across three sessions\, we'll demystify housing syst
 ems\, share college funding strategies\, and reflect on what helped us ge
