 \;"><strong>Masking and it's impact:</strong> What is it\, how does it de
 velop\, and its long- and short- term consequences    </p></li><li><p sty
 le="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Assessment and referral:</strong> Best pr
 actices\, including timing\, developmentally sensitive testing\, ethical 
 and equity-informed considerations\, and neurodiversity-affirming languag
 e\, and Theory of Mind&#160\;    </p></li><li><p style="line-height: 1.5\
 ;"><strong>Treatment and Support:</strong> Nervous system–informed\, st
