SUMMARY:Moon Poppies Paint & Sip- Lazy Days Beaverton
DESCRIPTION:Pop Up Paint and Sip\nOrder some grub and grab a drink for this super fun and easy paint party experience!\n\nWe've got the long tables reserved for us as you walk in. This venue holds 15 painters.\n\n**Please arrive 10 minutes before start time.**\n\n[Carrie](https://www.carolinegreenart.com/) will be guiding you step-by-step to create this beautiful painting of a Poppies under a full moon!\n\nCheck out Lazy Days Beaverton menu [here](https://lazydaysbrewing.com/portland-lazy-days-brewing-co-food-menu-beaverton)\n\nAll materials for your painting are included!\n**Tickets $40**\nNo experience necessary\, judgment free zone!\n(\\*Food and Drink NOT provided\, but you are welcome to buy)\nEXTRA TICKETS HERE: [https://www.paintandsipportland.com/](https://www.paintandsipportland.com/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pop-up-paint-and-sip/events/313704946/
