SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Abigail Krawson at Pendleton
DESCRIPTION:Opera singer Abigail Krawson will be performing at Pendleton on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Opera singer Abigail Krawson will be performing at Pioneer Place on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Acclaimed as “bewitching\,” having “her own soubrette-ish delivery\,” as well as “wringing every bit of sentiment out of her aria\,” Abigail Krawson is garnering critical and audience praise for her energetic and heartfelt operatic portrayals. She is on the roster of both The Portland Opera Chorus and The Portland Symphonic Choir\, the Director of Children and Youth Choirs at Lake Grove Presbyterian Church\, the Communications Director for Renegade Opera\, a private voice and piano teacher\, and also maintains an active solo calendar in and around Portland. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE.
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-abigail-krawson-at-pendleton/
LOCATION:Pendleton\, 825 SW Yamhill St\, Portland\, OR\, 97205\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PMMI_Social-Media_General.jpg
END:VEVENT
