SUMMARY: 28th Annual Furball - Purrtty In Pink
DESCRIPTION:FCCO is hosting our 28th Annual Furball and it’s gonna be a t
 otally awesome ’80s prom night!\n\nDust off that glam formalwear and get 
 ready to party. The Furball is our biggest fundraiser of the year\, provi
 ding critical funding for our spay/neuter services. Last year we cared fo
 r a record 8\,839 cats\, and we just celebrated our 150\,000th milestone 
 cat\, too. Whoa\, right? Your support keeps our compassionate work rockin
 ’. With big hair and hearts\, we hope you’ll be there!\n\nFCCO is seeing 
 a sustained increase in the need for affordable spay/neuter services for 
 homeless cats\, making your help more important than ever. To continue to
  be accessible to over 8\,000 cats each year who have no other options\, 
 we rely on broad community support. When you support Purrtty In Pink you 
 are partnering with one of the largest donation-based feral cat spay/neut
 er programs in the nation and preventing innumerable future litters of ki
 ttens from living on the streets.\n\nFor those of you who are not able to
  attend in person\, check out our online auction at feralcats.com http://
 feralcats.com - we’ll have some great items for you to bid on!\n
CATEGORIES:
