SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Johnny Franco and His Real Brother Dom at Nordstrom
DESCRIPTION:Johnny Franco and his Real Brother Dom will be performing at Nordstrom on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Walk down any street in Portland\, Oregon and you are sure to encounter a mustachioed Brazilian rock and roll troubadour named Johnny Franco and (his real brother) Dom. Recently moving from Sao Paulo\, the duo has developed a cult following in Portland for their high energy performance and music. The self-proclaimed Professional Entertainer has sold out his last two headline shows at the Doug Fir in Portland\, Oregon.
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-johnny-franco-and-his-real-brother-dom-at-nordstrom-4/
LOCATION:Nordstrom @ SW Morrison & Broadway\, 701 SW Broadway St.\, Portland\, OR\, 97205\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Johnny-Franco2-1-scaled.jpg
