SUMMARY:May Hillsboro Art Walk- FREE EVENT
DESCRIPTION:Pop Up Paint and Sip\nHillsboro art walk 2026- Get out and do something artsy/fun\, for FREE\n​​\n[​](https://hillsboroartwalk.com/)\nJoin me (and dozens of other artists) on May 5th at [Resolu Cellars](https://resolucellars.com/) and June 2nd at [Ancora Wellness](https://ancorawellness.com/) in Downtown Hillsboro for Art Walk!\n​\nI’ll be showcasing and selling my original\, hand‑painted artwork. This is a great chance to see my paintings up close\, chat with me about my creative process\, and find a piece that speaks to you. I’d love to meet you and share my newest work in person.\n\n**\\*\\*ALSO\, Check out my mural next door to this location! You can't miss it.**\n​\n[Find out more here](https://hillsboroartwalk.com/)\n​\nHillsboro’s Art Walk is a grassroots-organized event produced by local businesses and creative spaces invested in art\, creativity\, and community connection. Let live music carry you along Main Street and the Avenues as you discover local artists\, explore unique restaurants and boutiques\, and enjoy the night with friends and neighbors.\n​\nHillsboro Art Walk is a free\, all-ages event presented with support from Hillsboro’s Cultural Arts District and local nonprofit\, Influence Music Hall. Art Walk will celebrate its 20th Anniversary on Tuesday\, September 1st\, 2026. Every month.\n​\nArt Walk features:\n\n* Local galleries and art spaces\n* Live music\n* Performances\n* Food & Drink\n* Shopping\n* More!\n* [Additional Info Here](https://www.hillsboro-oregon.gov/our-city/departments/parks-recreation/events/art-walk)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pop-up-paint-and-sip/events/313715143/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260309T174358Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T174358Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/4/6/7/600_533121607.jpeg
END:VEVENT
