SUMMARY:Strategic Planning Updates and Employee Input
DESCRIPTION:Portland Community College supports student success by delive
 ring access to quality education while advancing economic development and
  promoting sustainability in a collaborative culture of diversity\, equit
 y\, and inclusion.  Join us for an update on our Strategic Planning proje
 cts and our shift to an annual review process. This new process is design
 ed to ensure our plan remains relevant and responsive to the evolving nee
 ds of our college.AgendaNew student onboarding update  Guided Pathways 
  program mapping update  Strategic course scheduling update  Increase sc
 holarships and wrap-around supports update  Capacity analysis  College-wi
 de goal setting  Questions and wrap-up  Next session announcement – Oct
 ober 8\, 2026
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Portland Community College supports stu
 dent success by delivering access to quality education while advancing ec
 onomic development and promoting sustainability in a collaborative cultur
 e of diversity\, equity\, and inclusion.</p><p>  Join us for an update on
  our Strategic Planning projects and our shift to an annual review proces
 s. This new process is designed to ensure our plan remains relevant and r
 esponsive to the evolving needs of our college.</p><p><strong>Agenda</str
 ong></p><ul><li>New student onboarding update  </li><li>Guided Pathways 
  program mapping update  </li><li>Strategic course scheduling update  <
 /li><li>Increase scholarships and wrap-around supports update  </li><li>C
 apacity analysis  </li><li>College-wide goal setting  </li><li>Questions 
 and wrap-up  </li><li>Next session announcement – October 8\, 2026  </l
 i></ul>
