SUMMARY: FREE Lunchtime Concert: Tualatin Valley OMTA
DESCRIPTION:TOC presents Lunchtime FREE Concerts every FIRST and THIRD We
 dnesday of the month at Noon. Our gift to the community for over 56 years
 \, join us in person or on our Youtube Channel. https://www.youtube.com/c
 hannel/UCLiO4ZclyOFIe8HiOFzWJyg\n\nThe Tualatin Valley Oregon Music Teach
 ers Association’s mission is to promote of the art of music\, the advance
 ment of musical education\, and the appreciation of music among the peopl
 e of the community.\n\nThey are affiliated with the Music Teachers Nation
 al Association (MTNA)\, the oldest professional organization of independe
 nt and collegiate music teachers in the United States.\n\nTheir district 
 comprises of approximately 85 professional musicians\, and offers lessons
  with a private piano teacher or an instructor of voice\, strings\, organ
 \, or guitar.\n\nFor more information\, check out their website: http://t
 vomta.org/ https://tvomta.org/ tvomta.org/\n\n\nWATCH THE LIVESTREAM! htt
 ps://youtube.com/live/himrs1QiLU0
