SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Gabe Hess at Sixth+Main
DESCRIPTION:Gabe Hess will be performing at Sixth+Main on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Gabe Hess is a singer/songwriter\, composer\, and arranger based out of the Pacific Northwest. Gabe first began working in the music industry during his college years\, performing in clubs in Boise Idaho with several different bands and collaborations. In 2018\, Gabe released his first EP titled “Working” which was comprised of an eclectic group of original songs spiced with styles from country to classic soul. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-gabe-hess-at-sixthmain-2/
LOCATION:SW 6th Ave & SW Main St\, Portland\, OR 97205\, SW 6th Ave & SW Main St\, Portland\, OR\, 97205\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Gabe-Hess.jpg
END:VEVENT
