 https://graduate.lclark.edu/programs/continuing_education/transactive/" t
 arget="_blank" rel="noopener">TransActive</a> we are working to strengthe
 n the systems that surround trans and gender diverse youth. This workshop
  will help participants to build a clear understanding of the current pol
 itical climate we are experiencing\, and discuss how we can leverage effe
 ctive communication\, liberatory practices\, and community engagement to 
 support trans lives in this moment.</p><h3 style="line-height: 1.5\;"><st
 rong>During the workshop participants will:</strong></h3><h4 style="line-
