SUMMARY:Coming Soon: Drive2Thrive Grand Prix!
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Sylvania campus to celebrate the end of the fi
 rst year of the Drive2Thrive program! Enjoy FREE ice cream with Poppie an
 d check out the BRAND NEW CAR that one lucky PCC student will win! Check 
 out the other amazing prizes and learn more about signing-up for Drive2Th
 rive here: pcc.edu/d2t*This event is FREE and in-person only. Only PCC st
 udents currently taking classes may participate. Supplies are limited and
  will be offered on a first-come\, first-served basis at the time of the 
 event. We cannot ship items to students and/or set items aside to be pick
 ed up later.The office of Student Engagement is pleased to offer accommod
