SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – MC Shoehorn at Pioneer Place
DESCRIPTION:MC Shoehorn will be performing at Pioneer Place on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Shoehorn began his musical journey in 1979 as a street performer in New Orleans\, where he got his first pair of tap shoes. He went on to perform in 30 countries and most of the USA\, and has released 6 full-length CDs featuring tap dance on his original compositions and his arrangements of show tunes. He plays a lot of instruments but is best known for simultaneously playing sax and tap dancing. \n 
