SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – JoAnna Lee at Pioneer Place
DESCRIPTION:Pop singer-songwriter and guitarist JoAnna Lee will be performing at Pioneer Place on Downtown’s Transit Mall! JoAnna brings a unique array of influences to her rootsy soul sound. When all her friends in grade school were getting into N’SYNC and Britney Spears\, her mother was introducing her to Stevie Wonder. Surrounded by a family full of cousins who all played instruments\, she took naturally to incorporating R&B (her original dream was to be a Motown singer) with her acoustic guitar. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-joanna-lee-at-pioneer-place-3/
LOCATION:Pioneer Place Main Entrance\, 700 SW 5th Ave\, Portland\, OR\, 97204\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/JoAnna_Lee.jpg
END:VEVENT
