 @lclark.edu">access@lclark.edu</a> with any additional questions or conce
 rns.</p></div></li></ul></div><hr /><h2><strong>About the Instructor</str
 ong></h2><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><picture class="lw_image lw_image7
