DESCRIPTION:\nCourtesy of NUNO\, photographer Hayashi Masayuki.\n\n\n\nJoin us for this autumn reception in the Pavilion Gallery to preview the NUNO Textile exhibition. We will serve light bites and refreshments. RSVP is required\; please contact developmentrsvp@japanesegarden.org\n\n\n\nIf you are interested in joining the Golden Crane Recognition Society\, contact our Philanthropy Manager\, Kalei Augustine at 503-542-9374 or kaugustine@japanesegarden.org.\n\n\n\nLearn more information about individual and corporate Golden Crane Recognition Society.\n\n\n\nMore details coming soon!\n\n\n
