  all day https://www.portland.gov/transportation/parking/smartpark&#13\;
 \n&#13\;\n## Coffee:&#13\;\nCapital One Café has drip coffee and fixings
  available for it&#13\;\n## Agenda:&#13\;\n&#13\;\n10 AM - Arrival: Head
