SUMMARY:Night Of A Thousand Cranes
DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\n\nNight Of A Thousand Cranes is an invitation-only event for Golden Crane Recognition Society members at the Founders Level ($5\,000) and above.\n\n\n\nThis evening event at Portland Japanese Garden celebrates the organization’s leadership donors and includes a cocktail hour followed by a seated dinner from Devil’s Food Catering.\n\n\n\nIf you are a Golden Crane Recognition Society member at the Founders Level and above\, please join us for a memorable evening of connection\, celebration\, and cultural inspiration set against the backdrop of the Garden.\n\n\n\nTo attend please RSVP to&nbsp\;developmentrsvp@japanesegarden.org or (503) 542-9307 by Friday\, October 9 with your meal choice\, and please note any dietary restrictions for members of your party.\n\n\n\nIf you are interested in joining the Golden Crane Recognition Society\, contact our Philanthropy Manager\, Kalei Augustine\, at 503-542-9374 or kaugustine@japanesegarden.org\n
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://wpmedia.japanesegarden.org/w:1600/h:1067/q:mauto/process:3956/id:e4076d5ffe1a2f6bc5d619513032e349/https://japanesegarden.org/Jonathan-Ley_Night-of-1000-Cranes-2014-2014-09-18-RS14524_thousand-cranes-28.jpg
