DESCRIPTION:Thanks to Roseline Coffee for providing a physical location! 
 Find inside the hotel and to the right\, likely on the couches&#13\;\n&#
 13\;\nCoffee\, bagels and people working on their careers and code! We h
 ave 2-5 mentors every month ready to help people get started in the indu
 stry\, get help with a particular problem\, or get career advice. We off
 er resume reviews\, portfolio reviews\, and sometimes mock interviews (t
 ime permitting).&#13\;\n&#13\;\nOnline Teams Link: https://teams.microso
